reference: Otherwise, this is it.

reference: Then please send me the number for the sideboard.

source: I will get the number for you and send this through via email.

mt: And that with the voucher??
reference: And that with the voucher???

source: Sonst bin ich als Kunde weg?!

source: Immerhin habe ich eine defekte Lieferung erhalten und jetzt dafür den vollen Preis bezahlt.

source: Dann werde ich das auch entsprechend bewerten!

reference: Then I will also evaluate this accordingly!

source: When was the voucher produced please?

reference: Wann wurde der Gutschein bitte ausgestellt?

source: Ich habe ihn eben nicht erhalten und daher auch nicht einlösen können weshalb ich endlich mal nachgefragt habe.
mt: I didn't receive it and therefore couldn't cash it, which is why I finally asked.
reference: I just didn't get it and therefore I couldn't redeem it, which is why I finally asked.

source: Durch Corona hatte ich letztes Jahr ganz andere Probleme und nie Zeit dafür.
mt: Through Corona I had quite different problems last year and never had time for it.
reference: Through Corona I had completely different problems last year and never time for it.

source: Und jetzt hieß es er sei abgelaufen was mich sehr verärgert.
mt: And now I was told that it had expired, which made me very angry.
reference: And now it was said he had expired, which annoyed me very much.

source: Schauen Sie in den Chat es ging um die Asare Sitzbank.

reference: Look into the chat it was about the Asare seat.

mt: Thank you.

reference: If you extend the voucher to me, then I will place a larger order immediately, but after all I kept the damaged piece of furniture and did not return it.

source: Und dass das vergangene Jahr anders als gedacht verlief konnte ich nicht ahnen und habe es eben nicht zeitgerecht einlösen und klären können.

reference: And that the past year was different than expected I could not guess and just could not redeem it in time and clarify it.
